E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Cape Feare: When Sideshow Bob is released from prison after sending Bart threatening letters, the Simpsons are moved to Terror Lake under the witness relocation programme. (S5 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Kids Are All Fight: When Homer finds an old roll of film and has it developed, the family take a trip down memory lane to when Bart and Lisa were always fighting. (S26 Ep19/22)

E4Plus1.uk.description: Lori Goldstein: The models are treated to new dos at a swanky salon in LA, but one of them leaves angry. A group photo shoot on a farm is imperilled by a pimple. (S16 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fish Guts Displacement: Sheldon begrudgingly takes care of Amy when she is sick. Bernadette arranges for Howard to go on a fishing trip with her macho father. (S6 Ep10)
